Retrieve operation of resource: igp-information

node-identifier: string
in path

ID of node-identifier

200 OK
PCE-IGP-INFO-BAG

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{
  "domain-identifier": "integer",
  "node-id": {
    "ls-identifier": "integer",
    "autonomous-system-number": "integer",
    "igp": {
      "bgp": {
        "confed-asn": "integer",
        "router-id": "string"
      },
      "ospf": {
        "router-id": "string",
        "area": "integer"
      },
      "igp-id": "string",
      "isis": {
        "system-id": "string",

      }
    }
  }
}

Schema Definitions

PCE-ERO-INFO:

ERO information

computed-metric-value: integer

Computed Metric Value

reported-metric-type: integer

Reported Metric Type

computed-rsvp-path: PCE-RSVP-HOP-TYPE

Computed RSVP path

PCE-RSVP-HOP-TYPE
computed-sr-path: PCE-SR-HOP-TYPE

Computed SR path

PCE-SR-HOP-TYPE
reported-sr-path: PCE-SR-HOP-TYPE

Reported SR path

PCE-SR-HOP-TYPE
computed-hop-list-time: integer

Computed Hop List Time

reported-rsvp-path: PCE-RSVP-HOP-TYPE

Reported RSVP path

PCE-RSVP-HOP-TYPE
computed-metric-type: integer

Computed Metric Type

reported-metric-value: integer

Reported Metric Value

Example
{
  "computed-metric-value": "integer",
  "reported-metric-type": "integer",
  "computed-rsvp-path": [
    {
      "hop-address": "string"
    }
  ],
  "computed-sr-path": [
    {
      "local-addr": {
        "af-name": "string",
        "ipv4": "string",
        "ipv6": "string"
      },
      "mpls-label": "integer",
      "sid-type": "string",
      "remote-addr": {
        "af-name": "string",
        "ipv4": "string",
        "ipv6": "string"
      }
    }
  ],
  "reported-sr-path": [
    {
      "local-addr": {
        "af-name": "string",
        "ipv4": "string",
        "ipv6": "string"
      },
      "mpls-label": "integer",
      "sid-type": "string",
      "remote-addr": {
        "af-name": "string",
        "ipv4": "string",
        "ipv6": "string"
      }
    }
  ],
  "computed-hop-list-time": "integer",
  "reported-rsvp-path": [
    {
      "hop-address": "string"
    }
  ],
  "computed-metric-type": "integer",
  "reported-metric-value": "integer"
}

              "computed-metric-value": "integer",
              "reported-metric-type": "integer",
              "computed-rsvp-path": [
                {
                  "hop-address": "string"
                }
              ],
              "computed-sr-path": [
                {
                  "local-addr": {
                    "af-name": "string",
                    "ipv4": "string"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}

association-infos_schema:

Associaition database in XTC

association-info: object[]

PCE Association information

    PCE-ASSO-BAG
type: string unknown, link, node, srlg

Type

group-id: integer

Group ID

sub-id: string

Sub ID

Example

  "association-info": [
    {
      "type": "string",
      "group-id": "integer",
      "sub-id": "string",

        {
          "lspid": "integer",

          "pce-based": "boolean"
        }
      ],
      "strict": "boolean",
      "association-type": "integer",
      "association-id": "integer",
      "association-source": {
        "af-name": "string",
        "ipv4": "string",
        "ipv6": "string"
      }
    }
  ]

cspf_schema:

CSPF path info

cspf-paths: object

This table models the path calculation capabilities in XTC.A GET operation for the complete table will return no entries.

cspf-path: object[]

A GET operation on this class returns the path .

    PCE-PATH-LIST-BAG
af: integer

Address Family

metric-type: integer

Metric type

shortest-path: integer

Whether path 1 or 2 should be shortest

source2: string

Source of path 2

disjoint-level: integer

Disjointness level

source1: string

Source of path 1

disjoint-strict: integer

Strict disjointness required

destination1: string

Destination of path 1

destination2: string

Destination of path 2

Example
{
  "cspf-paths": {
    "cspf-path": [
      {
        "af": "integer",
        "metric-type": "integer",
        "shortest-path": "integer",
        "source2": "string",
        "disjoint-level": "integer",
        "source1": "string",
        "disjoint-strict": "integer",
        "destination1": "string",
        "destination2": "string",
        "iterations-done": "integer",
        "cspf-result": "string",
        "output-path": [
          {
            "hops": [
              {
                "ipv4-prefix": "string",
                "address-family": "integer",
                "ipv6-prefix": "string"
              }
            ],
            "source": {
              "af-name": "string",
              "ipv4": "string",
              "ipv6": "string"
            },
            "destination": {
              "af-name": "string",
              "ipv4": "string",
              "ipv6": "string"
            },
            "cost": "integer"
          }
        ],
        "headends-swapped": "string"
      }
    ]
  }
}
